      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «اَلصَّلاَةُ ثَلاَثَةُ أَثْلاَثٍ ثُلُثٌ طَهُورٌ وَ ثُلُثٌ رُكُوعٌ وَ ثُلُثٌ سُجُودٌ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.66 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"The prayer consists of three parts: one-third is for purification, one-third is for bowing (ruku), and one-third is for prostration (sujud) \""
        ]
      }
